      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:26:21",
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) عَنِ الرَّجُلِ يَقْذِفُ الْجَارِيَةَ الصَّغِيرَةَ قَالَ لَا يُجْلَدُ إِلَّا أَنْ تَكُونَ قَدْ أَدْرَكَتْ أَوْ قَارَبَتْ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from one of his companions, from Aasim Bin Humeyd, from Abu Baseer who said, ",
          "‘I asked Abu Abdullah <sup>asws</sup> about the man who slanders the young girl. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘He would not be whipped except if she happens to have matured or near to it’."
        ]
      }
    },
